Which bits of MovieFS to build when
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
FrontEnd:   required for desktop builds only

KickStart:  always include

MFSRA:      only include if RealAudio is required

MFSRes:     always include; build with OPTIONS="" , OPTIONS="FrontEnd" ,
            OPTIONS="RealAudio" or OPTIONS="FrontEnd RealAudio" as appropriate

MovieFSMod: always include

PNAMod:     only include if RealAudio is required

TrueRecog:  always include; build with OPTIONS="" , OPTIONS="-DCinepak" ,
            OPTIONS="-DRPZA" or OPTIONS="-DCinepak -DRPZA" as appropriate
